title: Cant get into league need help
body: after i tried the update my lol file got corrupted, so I redownloaded it and now when I press launch  nothing happens  after, id appreciate some help

replies.body: Give your pc a good restart in case something crashed in the back ground.  Otherwise, your settings might have changed to now block the patcher from launching.  The steps in the [permissions](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions) guide should help fix that!
thx man ill give it a try, ill keep you updated
